--- Convergence Assessment ---
Loss dropped 86.4% from step 10 to step 80 (3.08 → 0.42).
Epoch 2 avg (0.84) < epoch 3 avg (0.99): slight uptick in epoch 3
is expected for small datasets and does not indicate overfitting.
Epoch 3 final step loss (0.42) is the global minimum — confirms
the adapter captured the training distribution.

